Requirements:
	boost 1.44(or later):
		download and install guide:http://www.boost.org/users/history/version_1_44_0.html
	threadpool 0.2.5(or later):
		download and install guide:http://threadpool.sourceforge.net/ ,OR simply download the necessary threadpool source code from our project site:http://code.google.com/p/stupidalgorithm/downloads/detail?name=threadpool-0_2_5-src.zip&can=2&q=

testing environment:
	Linux:
	Ubuntu 11.04+Eclipse CDT 8.0+boost 1.44+threadpool 0.2.5,CDT project files under 			linux_specific/CDT_Project directory.
	Windows:
	Win7+Visual Studio 2010 SP1+boost 1.44+threadpool 0.2.5,VC2010 project files under win_specific/VS2010 directory.

usage:
	type 'stupidalgorithm --help' in your command-line console for detail